        </div>

        <RequestQuoteForm client:load bg_color="bg-[#61798F]" />

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl bg-cover" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1557271904/Map_Screen_Shot.png")'
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#297CA3]/[.50] flex flex-col items-center py-4 px-6 gap-4 justify-evenly">
                <h2 class="flex flex-row items-center text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-white font-medium gap-2 bg-neutral-800/[.75] p-2 rounded-xl text-center ">Alder Home Security Works With Miami</h2>

                <p class="text-white bg-neutral-800/[.85] text-sm md:text-base w-full md:w-2/3 p-4 leading-6 ">Miami has specific needs when it comes to finding the best home security system. This is why Miami always looks to Alder for their service. Alder works hard to ensure their customers are satisfied, happy, and taken care of. In Miami, Alder focuses on what the city needs rather than general needs of the general customer. Their home security systems that are tailored to the customers home and to the customer's needs. Alder’s goal is to make sure the customer knows that they have everything that they need to feel secure. They set up the alarm in the home, the cameras, and everything else they need in order to make that happen for the customer. Because of that, Alder is the best home security Orlando.</p>
        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-cover bg-center " style={{
            backgroundImage: `url(${yardSign})`
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-neutral-800/[.75] md:bg-neutral-800/[.45] flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 py-8 px-4 md:px-12">

            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl">Why Alder is the</h3>

            <h3 class="text-white text-4xl font-medium">Best Home Security Orlando</h3>

            <p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium md:w-1/2 leading-6">There are a few reasons why Alder is the best home security Orlando. They offer doorbell cameras that allow you to have two-way communication through the doorbell. The great thing about this aspect of the security system is that it allows you to have access to your front step matter where you are in the world. You can access the camera through the ease of your phone. This is one of the aspects of the home security system that Miami loves. Alder also makes an effort to keep their services cheap while other security companies can overprice their products. Alder ensures to keep their services within the budget so every person in Miami can afford the service.
