            <div class="w-full h-[250px] bg-cover" style={{
                backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/v1557333574/simple.jpg")',
                backgroundPosition: "center 85%"
            }} />

            <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 md:gap-0 md:flex-row px-4 py-12 ">

                <div class=" w-full md:w-[25%] flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-4">
                    <h3 class="text-[#58585B] font-medium text-2xl text-center md:text-left ">Local Home Security</h3>

                    <p class="text-[#58585B] text-xl text-start" >In Miami and Orlando</p>
                </div>

                <p class="text-[#58585B] text-sm leading-6 w-full md:w-[65%] " >
                    Alder likes to keep things local for their customer. Living in Miami and Orlando, customers have local representatives in their area. They will be protected at all times of the day or night. The alarm systems are also some of the best on the market. Customers are able to monitor their cameras and sensors from a remote location. The customer will have full access to the alarm system, locks, and cameras. The reason why Alder does this is that they want the customer to have control of their home.
                    The systems are easy to control, safe, and give you the comfort of being in control at all times. You no longer have to worry or run home when you think you’ve forgotten to lock the door because you have access to everything on your phone. Alder works hard to put the customer in control of a local service. With Alder, the customers are in charge.
                </p>

